Titolo: Constantine (video game)

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Constantine is an action-adventure video game developed by Bits Studios and published by SCi Games in 2005 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 2, Xbox, and Mobile phone.
It is a movie tie-in license of the Warner Bros. film Constantine, in turn inspired by the Vertigo / DC Comics comic book series, Hellblazer.
Tilda Swinton, Gavin Rossdale and Max Baker reprised their roles from the film.

